Download instructions:
======================
1.   Go to ftp://ftp.genome.jp/pub/kegg/release/current/
1.1. Download the files kgml.tar.gz, ligand.tar.gz and genes.tar.gz into this directory.
1.2. Extract the three tarball files into this directory
2.   Go to ftp://ftp.genome.jp/pub/kegg/genes/genome
2.1  Save its contents into this directory.
3.   Go to tp://ftp.genome.jp/pub/kegg/genes/ko
3.1  Save its contents into this directory.

Your directory listing should now look like this:

total 4048592
